ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of LORRAINE ANDERSON as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Chad, with residence in Yaoundé; LORRAINE DIGUER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Tunisia; SARA NICHOLLS as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Mozambique, with concurrent accreditation as High Commissioner for Canada in the Kingdom of Eswatini, with residence in Maputo; and ELISE RACICOT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Portuguese Republic.
